column2: "Oh you? Are you ready yet? Not quite I guess."
"Where's Zeno? He's not with you? If he were I could have some fun."
"Tch. I wish I had someone to fight with right now. How boring."
"For him to not do anything at an important time. How typical of him! Fwahaha!"
"That guy hasn't changed at all. Really makes you want to laugh."
"I wonder who you'll turn out like. Me or Zeno?"
"It does no good to ask me. I have no interest in Master Gettemhart and Zeno's relationship."
